ica, Inter Reges Angli\u00e6, Et Alios Quosvis Imperatores, Reges, Pontifices, Principes, Vel Communitates |url=https://archive.org/details/fderaconventione01ryme |volume=1, pts. 1\u20132 |publisher=Joannem Neaulme |location=The Hague |ol=23299419M |ref=ZZZR4 }}\n*{{cite book |editor-last=Shirley |editor-first=WW |editor-link=Walter Waddington Shirley |year=1862 |title=Royal and Other Historical Letters Illustrative of the Reign of Henry III |url=https://archive.org/details/royalotherhistor01shir |volume=1 |series=Rerum Britannicarum Medii \u00c6vi Scriptores |publisher=Longman, Green, Longman, and Roberts |location=London |ref=ZZZS13 }}\n*{{cite book |editor-last=Sinclair |editor-first=J |editor-link=Sir John Sinclair, 1st Baronet |year=1795 |title=The Statistical Account of Scotland |url=https://archive.org/details/statisticalacco12sincgoog |volume=16 |publisher=William Creech |location=Edinburgh |ref=ZZZS10 }}\n*{{cite book |year=n.d. |editor1-last=Simpson |editor1-first=GG |editor2-last=Galbraith |editor2-first=JD |title=Calendar of Documents Relating to Scotland |url=https://archive.org/details/calendarofdocu05grea |volume=5 |publisher=[[Scottish Record Office]] |ref=ZZZS5 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1839 |editor-last=Stevenson |editor-first=J |editor-link=Joseph Stevenson |title=Chronicon de Lanercost, M.CC.I.\u2013M.CCC.XLVI |url=https://archive.org/details/chronicondelaner00stevuoft |publisher=[[The Bannatyne Club]] |location=Edinburgh |ol=7196137M |ref=ZZZS14 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1977 |origyear=1888 |editor-last=Storm |editor-first=G |editor-link=Gustav Storm |title=Islandske Annaler Indtil 1578 |hdl=10802/5009 |hdl-access=free |publisher=Norsk historisk kjeldeskrift-institutt |location=Oslo |isbn=82-7061-192-1 |ref=ZZZS11 }}\n*{{cite book |year=1875 |editor-last=Sweetman |editor-first=HS |title=Calendar of Documents Relating to Ireland, Preserved in Her Majesty's Public Record Office, London, 1171\u20131251 |url=https://archive.org/details/calendarofdocume01g